TI  - Evaluating the Performance of Data-Driven Models Combined with IoT to Predict the Onion Yield under Different Irrigation Regimes
T2  - EGYPTIAN JOURNAL OF SOIL SCIENCE
LA  - English
KW  - IoT
KW  - ML models
KW  - Automatic Watering System
KW  - onion
KW  - crop water productivity
