TI  - Temporal variability of ENSO effects on corn yield at the central region of Argentina
T2  - INTERNATIONAL JOURNAL OF CLIMATOLOGY
LA  - English
KW  - NINO-SOUTHERN-OSCILLATION
KW  - EL-NINO
