TI  - Satellite-based data for agricultural index insurance: a systematic quantitative literature review
T2  - NATURAL HAZARDS AND EARTH SYSTEM SCIENCES
LA  - English
KW  - DIFFERENCE VEGETATION INDEX
KW  - BASIS RISK
KW  - SMALLHOLDER FARMERS
