TI  - How does targeted microcredit empower the economic resilience of rural households in the context of natural disasters?
T2  - FRONTIERS IN SUSTAINABLE FOOD SYSTEMS
LA  - English
KW  - targeted microcredit
KW  - poverty-eradicating households
