TI  - Rain, forests and farmers: Evidence of drought induced deforestation in Madagascar and its consequences for biodiversity conservation
T2  - BIOLOGICAL CONSERVATION
LA  - English
KW  - RISK ATTITUDES
KW  - INCOME
KW  - DIVERSIFICATION
KW  - STRATEGIES
KW  - INSURANCE
