TI  - Learning about TURFs and natural variability: Failure of surf clam management in Chile
T2  - OCEAN & COASTAL MANAGEMENT
LA  - English
KW  - MESODESMA-MACTROIDES
KW  - YELLOW CLAM
KW  - RECRUITMENT VARIABILITY
