TI  - Molecular survey of cattle ticks in Burundi: First report on the presence of the invasive Rhipicephalus microplus tick
T2  - PLOS ONE
LA  - English
KW  - BOOPHILUS-MICROPLUS
KW  - GENUS RHIPICEPHALUS
KW  - THEILERIA-PARVA
KW  - BORNE DISEASES
