TI  - Changes in Nitrogen-Related Performance Attributes of Winter Wheat Varieties Released Between 1950 and 2020 in Dryland Region of China
T2  - JOURNAL OF SOIL SCIENCE AND PLANT NUTRITION
LA  - English
KW  - Nitrogen application rate
