TI  - EVALUATION OF RISK FACTORS IN AGRICULTURE: AN APPLICATION OF THE ANALYTICAL HIERARCHICAL PROCESS (AHP) METHODOLOGY
T2  - CHILEAN JOURNAL OF AGRICULTURAL RESEARCH
LA  - English
