TI  - Transforming agriculture in China: From solely high yield to both high yield and high resource use efficiency
T2  - GLOBAL FOOD SECURITY-AGRICULTURE POLICY ECONOMICS AND ENVIRONMENT
LA  - English
KW  - Agricultural transformation
KW  - Intensification
