TI  - Transitions in agro-pastoralist systems of East Africa: Impacts on food security and poverty
T2  - AGRICULTURE ECOSYSTEMS & ENVIRONMENT
LA  - English
KW  - Climate change
KW  - Smallholders
KW  - Livestock
KW  - Diversification
