TI  - Floating objects in the open ocean: Unveiling modifications of the pelagic habitat induced by forest cover change and climate variations
T2  - GLOBAL ENVIRONMENTAL CHANGE-HUMAN AND POLICY DIMENSIONS
LA  - English
KW  - Drifting fish aggregating device
KW  - Lagrangian simulation
KW  - Tropical tuna
