TI  - Land suitability analysis for cocoa (Theobroma cacao) production in the Sunyani municipality, Bono region, Ghana
T2  - SMART AGRICULTURAL TECHNOLOGY
LA  - English
KW  - Cocoa land suitability
KW  - Analytical hierarchy process
