TI  - Diversification strategies have a stabilizing effect for income and food availability during livelihood shocks: Evidence from small-scale aquaculture-agriculture systems in Myanmar during the COVID-19 pandemic
T2  - AGRICULTURAL SYSTEMS
LA  - English
