TI  - Evaluate the impact of soil erosion on local food security during the rainy season in Libokemkem and Ebinat District, Northwestern Ethiopia: an application of the daily soil loss model (DSL)
T2  - MODELING EARTH SYSTEMS AND ENVIRONMENT
LA  - English
KW  - Daily Soil Loss model
