TI  - Heterogeneous impact of crop diversification on farm net returns and risk exposure: Empirical evidence from Ghana
T2  - CANADIAN JOURNAL OF AGRICULTURAL ECONOMICS-REVUE CANADIENNE D AGROECONOMIE
LA  - English
KW  - climate risk management
KW  - crop diversification
