TI  - Seasonal Analysis of Spatial Distribution Patterns and Characteristics of Sepiella maindroni and Sepia kobiensis in the East China Sea Region
T2  - ANIMALS
LA  - English
KW  - cephalopod
KW  - climate change
KW  - warm
KW  - spawn
KW  - nursery
