TI  - Factors comprising tolerance to high temperature induce floret sterility in rice (Oryza sativa L.) cultivars in paddy field under common agricultural practices in Cagayan, Philippines
T2  - FIELD CROPS RESEARCH
LA  - English
KW  - Anther dehiscence
