TI  - Assessment of solar geoengineering impact on precipitation and temperature extremes in the Muda River Basin, Malaysia using CMIP6 SSP and GeoMIP6 G6 simulations
T2  - SCIENCE OF THE TOTAL ENVIRONMENT
LA  - English
