TI  - Adaptation and potential uses of sorghum and pearl millet in alternative and health foods
T2  - COMPREHENSIVE REVIEWS IN FOOD SCIENCE AND FOOD SAFETY
LA  - English
CP  - Symposium on Food Technology for Better Nutrition
