TI  - Diversification of maize-based intercropping systems in tropical rainforest agroecosystem of Nigeria: productivity, profitability and soil fertility
T2  - FUTURE OF FOOD-JOURNAL ON FOOD AGRICULTURE AND SOCIETY
LA  - English
