TI  - Asynchronous Responses of Fish Assemblages to Climate-driven Ocean Regime Shifts between the Upper and Deep Layer in the Ulleung Basin of the East Sea from 1986 to 2010
T2  - OCEAN SCIENCE JOURNAL
