TI  - A STUDY ON THE ROLE OF HABITATS OF A TIDAL LAND RECLAMATION AREA FOR WINTER MIGRANTS IN KOREA
T2  - IRRIGATION AND DRAINAGE
LA  - English
KW  - reclamation area
KW  - freshwater lake
