TI  - Reducing water productivity gap by optimizing irrigation regime for winter wheat-summer maize system in the North China Plain
T2  - AGRICULTURAL WATER MANAGEMENT
LA  - English
KW  - Irrigation regime
KW  - Historical scenarios
KW  - Water productivity
KW  - Groundwater table change
